== Prerequisites ==
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:neovim-ppa/unstable
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install neovim
sudo apt-get install ripgrep
sudo apt-get install fd-find
sudo apt-get install npm

sudo npm install -g tree-sitter
sudo npm install -g tree-sitter-cli
sudo npm install -g neovim

pip3 install pynvim

install packer (see the packer README for most up-to-date command):
git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/wbthomason/packer.nvim\
 ~/.local/share/nvim/site/pack/packer/start/packer.nvim

== To check nvim health ==

:checkhealth

== To update packages ==
vim ~/.config/nvim/lua/markwell/packer.lua
:so
:PackerSync

== General ==
<leader>pv  - return to netrw directory listing
<C-d>       - go down half a page, without moving cursor
<C-u>       - go up half a page, without moving cursor
<leader>y   - yank to system clipboard
<leader>d   - cut to system clipboard
<leader>s   - change token under cursor in file (vim find-replace)
<leader>x   - make current file executable
gb          - go back (jump back to last cursor position)
<F8>        - rotate colorscheme
<F10>       - toggle paste mode

== Visual Mode ==
J           - move highlighted code up one line
K           - move highlighted code down one line

== Telescope ==
<leader>sl  - 'search local' - relative to current directory.
<leader>sg  - 'search git'   - relative to current git repo.
<leader>gl  - 'grep local'   - grep relative to current directory.
<leader>gg  - 'grep git'     - grep relative to git repo.
<leader>gr  - 'grep'         - uses 'grep-string' rather than 'live_grep'.

== Within the Telescope menu ==
<C-x> go to file selection as a split
<C-v> go to file selection as a vsplit
<C-t> go to a file in a new tab

== Fugitive ==
<leader>gs  - git status

== Harpoon ==
<leader>a   - add file to harpoon
<C-h>       - harpoon quick menu
<C-1>       - harpoon saved file 1
<C-2>       - harpoon saved file 2
<C-3>       - harpoon saved file 3
<C-4>       - harpoon saved file 4

== During LSP completion suggestion ==
<C-p>       - previous suggestion
<C-n>       - next suggestion
<C-y>       - confirm selection under cursor
<C-space>   - complete selection

== LSP ==
gd          - go to definition
K           - hover info about word under cursor
<leader>vws - view workspace symbol
<leader>vd  - view diagnostic info about this line
[d          - next diagnostic message
]d          - prev diagnostic message
<leader>vca - show list of code actions
<leader>vrr - show references to token under cursor
<leader>vrn - rename token under cursor
<C-h>       - get signature help for token under cursor
<leader>ff  - format file

== Treesitter ==
<leader>ts  - toggle treesitter playground (ast)

== UndoTree ==
<leader>u   - toggle undotree

== ZenMode ==
<leader>zz  - toggle zenmode
